228
00:15:38,781 --> 00:15:40,209
Espere por mim, Duean.

229
00:15:41,412 --> 00:15:42,456
Qual é o problema, Duean?

230
00:15:43,646 --> 00:15:44,473
Dueano.

231
00:15:44,829 --> 00:15:45,491
Dueano.

232
00:15:45,919 --> 00:15:47,030
Duean, vá devagar.

233
00:15:47,603 --> 00:15:48,469
Dueano!

234
00:15:50,057 --> 00:15:52,209
Bom dia, Duean e Meen.

235
00:15:52,459 --> 00:15:54,259
Bom dia, professor Namphueng.

236
00:16:01,156 --> 00:16:04,156
